Articles.Content: I was modding KSP like any "normal" human being when i stumbeled upon some unexpected errors, TweakScale said I had some problems so I contacted them but they said I would be better of seeking help in the BDA community since the bug was related to a  patch duplication on one of the engines.  I will post the .log file here just in case:https://drive.google.com/file/d/16PWqsQ7RiYgas4ks4RH-yW03oHPVwlzx/view?usp=sharing. Hope someone finds the time to help me!
